### Upload Blog Images
POST http://localhost:3000/blog/upload-images
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="images"; filename="image1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./path/to/image1.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--

###

### Create Blog Post with Multi-Language Support
POST http://localhost:3000/blog
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

{
  "author": "John Doe",
  "writingDate": "2025-11-06T10:00:00.000Z",
  "active": false,
  "translations": [
    {
      "language": "en",
      "title": "My First Blog Post",
      "htmlContent": "<h1>Welcome to My Blog</h1><p>This is my first blog post with <strong>HTML</strong> content.</p>"
    },
    {
      "language": "de",
      "title": "Mein erster Blog-Beitrag",
      "htmlContent": "<h1>Willkommen in meinem Blog</h1><p>Dies ist mein erster Blog-Beitrag mit <strong>HTML</strong>-Inhalt.</p>"
    },
    {
      "language": "fr",
      "title": "Mon premier article de blog",
      "htmlContent": "<h1>Bienvenue sur mon blog</h1><p>Ceci est mon premier article de blog avec du contenu <strong>HTML</strong>.</p>"
    },
    {
      "language": "it",
      "title": "Il mio primo post del blog",
      "htmlContent": "<h1>Benvenuti nel mio blog</h1><p>Questo è il mio primo post del blog con contenuto <strong>HTML</strong>.</p>"
    }
  ],
  "images": [
    {
      "url": "https://your-minio-url.com/blog/image1.jpg",
      "altText": "Blog header image"
    }
  ],
  "links": [
    {
      "url": "https://example.com/related-article",
      "title": "Related Article: How to Write Great Blogs"
    }
  ]
}

###

### Get All Blog Posts (Public)
GET http://localhost:3000/blog

###

### Get Only Active Blog Posts (Public)
GET http://localhost:3000/blog?activeOnly=true

###

### Get All Blog Posts in German
GET http://localhost:3000/blog?language=de

###

### Get Active Blog Posts in English
GET http://localhost:3000/blog?activeOnly=true&language=en

###

### Get Single Blog Post (Public)
GET http://localhost:3000/blog/YOUR_BLOG_ID

###

### Get Single Blog Post in French
GET http://localhost:3000/blog/YOUR_BLOG_ID?language=fr

###

### Update Blog Post - Add Italian Translation
PATCH http://localhost:3000/blog/YOUR_BLOG_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

{
  "translations": [
    {
      "language": "en",
      "title": "Updated Blog Post Title",
      "htmlContent": "<h1>Updated Content</h1><p>This content has been updated.</p>"
    },
    {
      "language": "de",
      "title": "Aktualisierter Blog-Beitrag-Titel",
      "htmlContent": "<h1>Aktualisierter Inhalt</h1><p>Dieser Inhalt wurde aktualisiert.</p>"
    },
    {
      "language": "it",
      "title": "Titolo del post del blog aggiornato",
      "htmlContent": "<h1>Contenuto aggiornato</h1><p>Questo contenuto è stato aggiornato.</p>"
    }
  ],
  "active": true
}

###

### Activate Blog Post
PATCH http://localhost:3000/blog/YOUR_BLOG_ID/activate
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

###

### Deactivate Blog Post
PATCH http://localhost:3000/blog/YOUR_BLOG_ID/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

###

### Delete Blog Post
DELETE http://localhost:3000/blog/YOUR_BLOG_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

###

### Complete Example: Create a Multi-Language Blog Post with Images and Links
